body_text.text: This bibliography is drawn from the journals listed at the end and is selected from a comprehensive bibliography that is compiled by immunologists and is available on diskette. The bibliography is based on literature entered into our database between 1st April 1994 and 31 st March 1995 (articles are generally added to the database about two and a half months after publication). In addition, the bibliography contains every paper annotated by reviewers; these references were obtained from a variety of bibliographic databases and published between the beginning of the review period and the time of going to press. The bibliography has been grouped into topics that relate to the reviews in this issue.
